{"tid":752665,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Momo@TWICE拍MV嘆天氣熱　Sana低胸扮海馬搞笑游水","createTime":"2018-07-23T04:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T04:47:37.000Z","uid":1086,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1966d5988b4b8dfe404e1447b9866b436810c7e6","tid":752665,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:10:12.000Z","msg":"TWICE九位成員Momo、周子瑜、娜璉、定延、Sana、志效、Mina、多賢和彩瑛早前在日本沖繩赤墓沙灘拍攝《Dance The Night Away》MV，TWICE難得以背心短褲等夏日服裝示人，特別是Sana向來以身材纖瘦見稱，今次更以低胸服裝拍攝，實在讓ONCE大飽眼福！不過，衣著清涼也難抵日本高溫，Momo、Mina和彩瑛等人不約而同感嘆天氣炎熱，彩瑛更直言希望下雨，未料竟一言成讖，TWICE和製作組惟有在帳篷等待雨後繼續拍攝，娜璉、志效等人大唱卡啦OK消磨時間，又罕有表演Rap，令現場氣氛變得歡樂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1667102/org/e0a439fd4d810e3ca4368b90bbef9421.jpg/OPrKygY-nd_q29DUc0wcQLtsWaa7fSZhzp6lZs6epWY?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1667102%2Forg%2Fe0a439fd4d810e3ca4368b90bbef9421.jpg%2FOPrKygY-nd_q29DUc0wcQLtsWaa7fSZhzp6lZs6epWY%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0d6f6461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>TWICE早前在日本拍攝《Dance The Night Away》MV。（影片截圖）</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1667103/org/ed12d0fda64ba8a1bf26ab059c793456.jpg/IFxoJ2X7vaO-iwl5Xff1nEDGmbuHMIlOBtf1ggbX9YI?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1667103%2Forg%2Fed12d0fda64ba8a1bf26ab059c793456.jpg%2FIFxoJ2X7vaO-iwl5Xff1nEDGmbuHMIlOBtf1ggbX9YI%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=903a7917&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>Momo嘆天氣非常炎熱，不知道因為定延用沙在她背上寫字？（影片截圖）</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1667100/org/6ad7f45e96158549217aed77e141530a.jpg/GXlUtI-k5OoV8IUwdIkOxKwF3ap5OoIULyB0_y8gdP8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1667100%2Forg%2F6ad7f45e96158549217aed77e141530a.jpg%2FGXlUtI-k5OoV8IUwdIkOxKwF3ap5OoIULyB0_y8gdP8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ceffed09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>彩瑛大叫「雨啊！來啊！」沒想到後來真的下了一場大雨，可算是TWICE的燈神了！（影片截圖）</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1667099/org/cb707469abfde99ea4bec6f6dd04c0b3.jpg/y0zjER6K8ay-zAiBxDwGIChObXI9ZznjTltMtE5bTLQ?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1667099%2Forg%2Fcb707469abfde99ea4bec6f6dd04c0b3.jpg%2Fy0zjER6K8ay-zAiBxDwGIChObXI9ZznjTltMtE5bTLQ%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=8b4f7a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>等待停雨期間，娜璉唱卡啦OK消磨時間。（影片截圖）</em><br />\n<br />\n停雨後，TWICE等人密鑼緊鼓繼續拍攝，其後九人拍攝嬉水戲份，TWICE寓工作於娛樂，成員之間互潑海水，非常歡快！完成MV工作後，TWICE心情相當舒暢，紛紛在水中游泳，ONCE可以在片段中可見TWICE的泳術：彩瑛以自由式見長，定延自爆沒有泳鏡不會游泳，而Sana的泳姿有如海馬， Momo目睹也立刻模仿，非常搞笑！相信ONCE可以透過TWICE的拍攝花絮，了解她們真實而自在的一面！"},{"pid":"8c301aeb11fbca80c2391a28c6213355c48592c2","tid":752665,"uid":51412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8fWe99c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F8fWe99c.jpg&h=d82a3e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/wrBkNCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FwrBkNCe.jpg&h=ca03dee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7093e953d39f3b758a3f0618bebf765187556582","tid":752665,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c301aeb11fbca80c2391a28c6213355c48592c2","tid":752665,"uid":51412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8fWe99c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F8fWe99c.jpg&h=d82a3e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/wrBkNCe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FwrBkNCe.jpg&h=ca03dee1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T04:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}